rows.name: Ask Yusof about H.B.

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0001
rows.name:
After that last incident, we Mediators have started
examining data about New LA residents more closely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0002
rows.name:
If someone in the city is acting even slightly out of the
ordinary, we're going to question them to make sure
they aren't an impostor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0003
rows.name:
It isn't going to be easy to expose beings who are so
skilled at mimicking humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0004
rows.name:
But the heightened scrutiny should put them on edge.
If we can stay vigilant for when they eventually slip up,
I'm confident that we'll find them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0009
rows.name:
Lara managed to keep his cool when he found
Clemons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0010
rows.name:
But as soon as we brought Clemons's body to the
storage area of the Mimeosome Maintenance Center,
he burst into tears.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0011
rows.name:
When we find the Lifehold Core, we'll be able to give
Clemons a new body, so there's no need to mourn.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0012
rows.name:
Lara kept apologizing for what Clemons went through,
even though it wasn't his fault. ...Heh. He may seem
rough and tumble, but he's a real softy at heart.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0013
rows.name:
But when Clemons does get resurrected into a new
body, I'm gonna have to train the crap out of him
so he doesn't slip up and get killed again![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0018
rows.name:
Ever since the Definians appeared, we Mediators have
started regarding everyone in New LA with suspicion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0019
rows.name:
...Is that guy real? ...Could she be an impostor?
...Is there anything strange about him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0020
rows.name:
Eventually we started to see the enemy in everyone,
even close friends. It was our duty to do it, but it was
an excruciating one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0021
rows.name:
So I really can't thank you enough for taking out their
boss. Because of that, we can finally start to relax.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0026
rows.name:
Ever since the Definians appeared, we Mediators
have started regarding everyone in New LA with
suspicion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0027
rows.name:
...Is that guy real? ...Could she be an impostor?
...Is there anything strange about him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0028
rows.name:
Earlier, I even heard a report of there being two
different Laras, and I was all ready to go hunt down
the Definian impostor...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0029
rows.name:
But to my shock, they were both real.
Lara has an actual twin brother![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG0030
rows.name:
But as I was questioning the younger brother,
it became clear he'd been to my room multiple times.
So which times was I actually with HIM?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG1001
rows.name:
Recently, Lara Nara has been going on and on about
how handsome some BLADE named "H.B." is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG1002
rows.name:
So I looked into the guy, and it turns out he's some
elite BLADE who aspires to be our next commander.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG1003
rows.name:
Lara's a pretty accomplished BLADE himself.
Could this "H.B." be using his position and pretty face
to get close to him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev019001_MSG1004
rows.name:
Dammit! I don't care how handsome or elite he may
beâ€”until Clemons gets back, I'm swatting any flies
that start buzzing around our Lara![ST:wait ]
